{
  "stem": "3631.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was three months after Hitler came to power, and it was a day in which all Jewish offices and all Jewish businesses and stores were boycotted.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was one SR man, the brownshirts, stood in front of the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here, this is a Jewish business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the day he put out his shingle, his office was boycotted, and he was smart.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He closed up his office the same day and went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- but otherwise, you keep on living your life because you hope-- you hope for the best.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You hope you'll keep on living and things will settle down and-- and straighten out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think everybody did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in order to do this-- it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the-- America had the immigration quotas going by-- by place of birth, and they were-- they were very limited, and, like, the German quota was very tight.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to have somebody in the United States who would sponsor you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other countries, some were-- most of them were difficult to get in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Shanghai was open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Cuba was open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think Argentina was open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there's one other thing you must not forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you live in a country-- you live all your life there, and you have your family there, and you have your business there, your friends there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have your roots there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It is not easy to get yourself up and break up everything you have, only in fear of something worse happening, and start completely new in a country where you probably did not speak the language, where you tear apart the family.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is probably the most difficult thing for people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not everybody can do this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of my father's sisters went to-- to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
